{"tid":2449853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國發現武肺病毒新變種能躲過標準檢測","createTime":"2021-03-17T03:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T17:33:13.000Z","uid":294518,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c4fd8346e496a0360bff9def924f18b68469adc3","tid":2449853,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:41:00.000Z","msg":"法國發現武肺病毒新變種能躲過標準檢測<br />\n<a href=\"https://nypost.com/2021/03/16/france-finds-new-covid-19-variant-that-escapes-detection/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2021%2F03%2F16%2Ffrance-finds-new-covid-19-variant-that-escapes-detection%2F&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=a8d1378f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nypost.com/2021/03/16/france-finds-new-covid-19-variant-that-escapes-detection/</a><br />\n<br />\n《紐約郵報》（New York Post）3月16日報導，法國發現新的中共病毒變體，但在PCR（聚合酶鏈反應）檢測中卻未被發現。<br />\n<br />\n在法國發現這個新的中共病毒變種，似乎能夠躲過病毒的標準檢測。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》援引France24報導，法國衛生部周一晚間表示，在布列塔尼大區的一個市鎮&mdash;&mdash;拉尼翁（Lannion）的一家醫院發現了一組新中共病毒變種的病例。<br />\n<br />\n衛生官員說，其中幾名患者的PRC檢測結果為陰性。<br />\n<br />\n據該媒體報導，巴斯德研究所的研究人員正在研究該變異體是否有基因修改，使其更難檢測。<br />\n<br />\n官員說，雖然可能更難追踪，但這種變異體似乎並不比其他變異體更嚴重或更容易傳播。<br />\n<br />\n據該媒體報導，在最新的中共病毒激增的情況下，平均每天新增病例超過2萬例，法國政府頂住了壓力，下令實施新的封鎖。"},{"pid":"f6900b246659bf22933ee38e5862171493138200","tid":2449853,"uid":294518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:42:32.000Z","msg":"據France24報導，法國總理讓&middot;卡斯特（Jean Castex）說，&ldquo;情況並沒有好轉，感染人數越來越多，醫院病人很多且負擔很重，很多病人的平均年齡越來越低，而且他們不一定有並發症。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n法廣（RFI）也於3月16日做了相關報導，法國衛生總局DGS週一宣布，在布列塔尼檢測發現一種中共病毒布列塔尼變種，目前正在調查評估其可傳播性和嚴重性。<br />\n<br />\n該報導稱，法國衛生總局在給健康業者的一個信息中進一步說明指出，經過法國巴斯德研究所（Pasteur Institute）進行的分析表明說&ldquo;很明顯地，這是一種在編碼S蛋白的區域以及其他病毒區域中攜帶9個突變&rdquo;。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E6%B3%95%E5%9B%BD/20210316-%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E6%B3%95%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E5%B8%83%E5%88%97%E5%A1%94%E5%B0%BC%E5%8F%98%E7%A7%8D%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Fcn%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259B%25BD%2F20210316-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259B%25BD%25E5%258F%2591%25E7%258E%25B0%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25A7%258D%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%2588%2597%25E5%25A1%2594%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E5%258F%2598%25E7%25A7%258D%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=b0a8476c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E6%B3%95%E5%9B%BD/20210316-%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E6%B3%95%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E5%B8%83%E5%88%97%E5%A1%94%E5%B0%BC%E5%8F%98%E7%A7%8D%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92</a>"},{"pid":"f50c2f01351f83e76cbdcbd9388fa039358a8ded","tid":2449853,"uid":37197,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:48:44.000Z","msg":"個肺炎真係好撚惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181fde064ab732e649f1506d16afd33276a0c681","tid":2449853,"uid":33222,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:49:46.000Z","msg":"法國又會被中共話係法國變種病毒了&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"c67dd1ac4d5bf8c4dd0b36ebbf1ec873875d8f14","tid":2449853,"uid":70964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c4fd8346e496a0360bff9def924f18b68469adc3","tid":2449853,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:41:00.000Z","msg":"法國發現武肺病毒新變種能躲過標準檢測<br />\n<a href=\"https://nypost.com/2021/03/16/france-finds-new-covid-19-variant-that-escapes-detection/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2021%2F03%2F16%2Ffrance-finds-new-covid-19-variant-that-escapes-detection%2F&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=a8d1378f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nypost.com/2021/03/16/france-finds-new-covid-19-variant-that-escapes-detection/</a><br />\n<br />\n《紐約郵報》（New York Post）3月16日報導，法國發現新的中共病毒變體，但在PCR（聚合酶鏈反應）檢測中卻未被發現。<br />\n<b